The '''scurrier disease''' was a dangerous affliction carried by [[Scurrier/Legends|scurriers]]. Any scurrier had a ten percent chance of carrying the disease, although the scurriers themselves were immune to it. Individuals bitten by an infected scurrier automatically caught the disease.<ref name="RaS" />

